    "abstractNote": "The purpose of this study is twofold. First, it sets the historical context in which Aphrahat wrote his Demonstrations and deals with the interesting relationship between his writings, \u2018against the Jews\u2019 and the Sassanian persecution of Christians. It also treats his refutation of the Jewish charges. Secondly, it addresses his \u2018unique\u2019 view of christology which is not in line with the Nicene decision concerning one aspect yet at the same time it is congruent with it. The paper also tries to point out that his view on christology was \u2018unique\u2019 but not exceptional in the Early Church.",
